
Placky is simple Realtime network interface monitoring system.

It is meant as a simple web version of iptraf. More features will be added to it soon :)

It consists of a simple Perl script, which is used to generate JSON data and and a simple web page to display the current interface usage.

Live Demo can be found here: http://goblin.yuhu.biz/placky/

Requirements:
* Perl
* JSON::XS perl module
* jQuery (it comes with 1.11.3)
* FlotCharts (it comes with 0.8.3)

Installations:
  Simply unpack it, configure the directories in install.sh and run ./install.sh

